title: War of the Roses: Boiling Chocolate Syrup
description: Nicole has been with her boyfriend Jamie for a over a year.  A few months ago Jamie landed himself in Urgent Care for an injury and his explanation of how he got the injury doesn't make a ton of sense to Nicole so now she's doing War of the Roses to try and figure out if he's a liar/cheater or really dumb.
